## Requirements

- Python 3.8+
- cryptography >= 3.0

## Optional Dependencies

- `asyncio` support: `pip install spindlex[async]`
- Development tools: `pip install spindlex[dev]`
- GSSAPI authentication: `pip install spindlex[gssapi]` (Unix only)

